In case they fail to do so, the money belongs to the village. Since the village is on the edge of collapse - the young are leaving, no perspective - this money could mean his salvation. The head of the local committee is Damir's father Mile, while his angry opponent is Sveto doing everything to sat on his position. The committee are also conservative ...

To make matters even worse, in the fight for Djura's million, are not unique. Tomislav was heavily influenced by his mother Milica and doing everything to Kreso and Katarina be eliminated as potential successors so that he has all the money for himself.

imdb.plot outline: Katarina's, Tomislav's and Kreso's grandfather dies. He leaves them a million euros, but they can get the money only if they stay in the same house that he grew up in for a year or the money goes to the village. People from the village find out, and try to get them to go away.
imdb.title: Kud puklo da puklo
